data.description: Affordable find with a convenient location. Plus, mountain views and private cul-de-sac! Open living room that's right by the kitchen. Kitchen features laminate wood flooring, an eat-in area, and a nice amount of cabinet storage. The master bedroom includes a mountain view. Also on the main level is an additional bedroom and full bathroom. The basement boasts a large family room with wood paneling. The 3rd bedroom has an attached half bath. Lastly, there is an unfinished room that includes storage space and the laundry facilities. The backyard is spacious with a large storage shed and mature trees. The concrete patio is the perfect place to set up some outdoor furniture and enjoy the peaceful backyard! One-car garage has back door leading to backyard. Solar panels are a great opportunity for savings. Check this one out soon!
